ack&#8217;s</a> Custom Content Types module to display portfolio projects in a contemporary Masonry grid.</p>\n<p>Designed by Automattic&#8217;s <a href="https://thomasguillot.com/">Thomas Guillot</a>, Orvis was inspired by the photographer wife of a colleague/friend, and named as a nod to their dog, <a href="http://mapandmenu.com/orvis-the-dog/">a sweet black Lab</a>.</p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/orvis/">Take Orvis for a ride</a> on your site today!</p>\n<p><a href="https://orvisdemo.wordpress.com/"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6608" src="https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/orvis-ss.png?w=840&#038;h=730" alt="Orvis screenshot" width="840" height="730" /></a></p><img alt="" border="0" src="https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=themeshaper.com&#038;blog=45531309&#038;post=6607&#038;subd=themeshaper&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:1:{s:7:"content";a:2:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:7:"\n			\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"url";s:82:"http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/88ff758a54124a679af2e4cdaae8ba62?s=96&d=identicon&r=G";s:6:"medium";s:5:"image";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:1:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"kathrynwp";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:7:"\n			\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"url";s:59:"http://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2016/07/orvis-ss.png";s:6:"medium";s:5:"image";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:1:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Orvis screenshot";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"